        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2003-08-29T21:09:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Helpers Job Opportunity Act - Provides for the creation of an additional category of laborers or mechanics known as helpers under the Davis-Bacon Act.</p> <p>Requires a helper of a laborer or mechanic to be paid the prevailing wage of helpers of laborers or mechanics employed on similar projects in the same subdivision of the State.]]></text>
      </summary>
